<item>
            <title>[WICKET-6642] Form.findSubmittingComponent returns null instead of SubmitLink</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6642</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a form is submitted by a SubmitLink, you can no longer find the submitting component using Form.findSubmittingComponent.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This was probably introduced by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-6348&quot; title=&quot;New FormComponentUpdatingBehavior to replace wantOnSelectionChangedNotifications()&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;WICKET-6348&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;WICKET-6348&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;ve attached a quickstart with the problem. I can confirm that it was introduced between 8.0.0 M5 and M6/&lt;/p&gt;</description>
